casebody.data:
STATE of New Jersey, Plaintiff-Movant,
v.
Rafael CAMEY, Defendant-Respondent. M-779 September Term 2017
080574 Supreme Court of New Jersey. June 22, 2018

ORDER

It is ORDERED that the motion for leave to appeal is granted; and it is further

ORDERED that the appellant may serve and file a supplemental brief on or before August 21, 2018, and respondent may serve and file a supplemental brief forty-five (45) days after the filing of appellant's supplemental submission, or, if appellant declines to file such a submission, on or before October 5, 2018.
